Cloud security mechanism is a specific technical control, software tool or process to implemented to enfroce security polices and protect cloud resource
i. SOS( single sign on)
ii. IAM( Identity and access management)
iii. Hashing
iv. Digital signature

Distater recovery is a polices, tool or procedure to enable the recovery or continuation of vital technology infrastructure and system following a natural or human-intended disaster.
Key
i. RTO( Recovery time objective)
ii. RPO ( Recovery point object)
iii. Geo-Redundancy
iv. Backup-stragegy
v. fail over mechanism
vi. disaster recovery as a service

Challenges in Cloud Security
i. lack of visibility and control
ii. data soverinity and complicance
iii. Shared technology issue
iv. Insecure API
v. Insider threat
vi. Account Hijacking
